      "citation": "Mease, P. J., Gladman, D. D., Papp, K. A., Khraishi, M. M., Thaci, D., Behrens, F., . . . Alvarez, D. (2013). Prevalence of rheumatologist-diagnosed psoriatic arthritis in patients with psoriasis in European/North American dermatology clinics. Journal of the American Academy of Dermatology, 69(5), 729–735. doi:10.1016/j.jaad.2013.07.023. PMID: 23981683. National Institute for Health and Care Excellence (NICE). (2017). Psoriasis: Assessment and management. Clinical guideline [CG153]. Published: 24 October 2012. London: NICE. [PhenX: https://www.phenxtoolkit.org/protocols/view/171801]",
